# Cursor Rules for Test Directory

## Test Files

- **ALWAYS use .ts (TypeScript) files for test scripts, NOT .js files**
- When creating or modifying tests, use TypeScript (.ts) files
- Prefer TypeScript for all new test files
- Only use .js files if absolutely necessary for compatibility

## Test Structure

- Tests should run serially with independent brokers on unique ports
- Each test should be isolated and not depend on other tests
- Test timeouts should be handled gracefully
- Use `LMX_TEST_PORT` environment variable for port assignment

